    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-02-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-02-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="140"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d140">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">MacVeagh</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-02-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 28, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Notify Italian minister for foreign affairs and Colombian minister to Italy that
                    the President accepts the joint invitation of the Governments of Italy and
                    Colombia to arbitrate the dispute between them growing-out of the claim of
                    Ernesto Cerruti. Formal instruction follows.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gresham.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
